Feeling left out, Adorabat wishes Mao Mao and Badgerclops would spend less time with each other and more time with her. When she gets
what she wishes for and accidentally breaks up their friendship, only the secret of their past can bring them back together.

description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

We soon learn that dear, sweet Chair was too good for this world.

description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 3 del episodio estreno.

description: Optimus struggles to recover from using the Matrix of Leadership while the Autobots attempt to get the Allspark back to Cybertron.

title: It Came From the Nightosphere
description: Against Marceline's wishes, Finn conjures her father, the Lord of Evil, and attempts to reconcile their rocky relationship. But when the Lord of Evil discovers his daughter has turned the family axe into a bass guitar, he takes it from her and starts sucking up all the souls in Ooo! Finn must find a way to stop the Lord of Evil and get Marceline's guitar back.

title: Neumaticos de la Fortuna
description: Las compras en la tienda de segunda mano del equipo Tennyson se ven interrumpidas por el último atraco a alta velocidad de LaGrange -que ahora cuenta con la ayuda de un auto de carreras electromagnético superrápido- y Ben debe convencer a Kevin 11 para que ayude a detener la ola de robos del trotamundos endemoniado con la velocidad.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Ene-amigos
description: Dos nuevos Peleadores Bakugan, Shun y Magnus, buscan ser parte de Los Fantásticos.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Area 51
description: A mysterious Galvan arrives and demands Blukic and Driba to give back a super powerful weapon needed to stop a threat to Earth.

title: Sugar Berry Fever
description: Mao Mao tries to hide his love of cobbler.

title: Princesa gotica
description: Gwen lleva por accidente un pony de peluche rosado que le encanta a la guardería, y pasa todo el día negando que es suyo.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Oct-Father
description: When Princess Morbucks steals Octi, Bubbles' reaction surprises everyone, even her sisters.

title: Baby Boi TP
description: Apple needs to acquire a lifetime supply of toilet paper to finish his modern art sculpture.

title: Diagrama de Vin
description: Cuando Ben ve que Vin Etanol se asombra con los conocimientos automovilísticos de Kevin, los celos de Ben lo convencen de que tiene que superar a Kevin antes de que el joven convenza a Vin de adoptar su lado malo en una carrera a beneficio.

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Brain Trust
description: Dr. Fox accidentally transports the gang inside her brain, where they must control her movements to complete a dangerous experiment.

title: El equipo Exit
description: Los Fantásticos compiten por el número de visitas en sus videos con un equipo rival llamado "El equipo Exit" en una batalla donde se juegan el todo por el todo.

title: Dance Reynaldo Dance
description: Vic is desperate to win the cash prize for the dance contest in Monte Macabre and is frustrated that his partner Val won't let him call all the shots. Instead he chooses a different partner: Reynaldo. But Vic pushes Reynaldo too hard to execute his artistic vision. Eventually he learns that in order to be a success, you have to be equal partners.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Video Store
description: Clarence, Jeff, and Sumo visit their local video store to rent a movie, but discover it's all rented out! Each of them have a different idea of what tape to bring home, and must enlist the help of a tie breaker to figure it out.

title: KO, Rad, and Enid!
description: When confronted with their lack of a team gimmick, KO, Rad, and Enid wonder what their group identity should be.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 2
description: WildWheel finds Optimus Prime rebuilding a small Cybertronian town, only to discover the Prime does not recognize him.

title: The Final Book
description: The last book of Kelsey's favorite fantasy series goes missing from the library, so Craig decides to help her solve the mystery of who took it.

title: Wristy Business
description: Beth and Leshawna try to one-up each other with fake injuries as they compete for the attention and sympathy of the other kids at daycare.

title: #La dulce justicia - Cuarta parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 4 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Public Radio
description: After listening to a public radio broadcast during class, Clarence is inspired to record a radio interview of his own featuring his buddy Sumo. When Ms. Baker hears the charming interview, she calls in a favor and gets Clarence a spot on the actual Aberdale Public Radio! The search is on - to find the perfect interview subject for his big day.

title: Camp Fear
description: When a race of alien mushrooms takes over a summer camp, Ben discovers a whole new alien to battle the menace.

title: Major Competition/Mr. Mojo's Rising
description: Major Competition: There's a new man in town, Major Man, a perfect superhero, who cuts in on the girls' turf. But the girls prove that even though they're minors, they're still the major part of saving the day./Mr. Mojo's Rising: Mojo kidnaps the Professor and forces him to give him the same superpowers at the girls. But once empowered, the true evolution of this supervillain chimp comes to light.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: Countdown
description: Axel has to clean up the living room in time for his uncle's dinner party, but trying to do too much at once leaves him stuck as a toy with Orangutank on the loose and less than an hour until the guests arrive.

title: Nean
description: Raven is cursed to be nice; meanwhile, Starfire is about to marry a pot of chili.

title: Agent of Destruction
description: DeBizz helps the Warriors become more famous as their agent, but Vambre returns to adventuring while Prohyas gets caught up in the DeBizz fame trap.

title: Vin Diagram
description: When Ben sees Vin Ethanol impressed with Kevin's automotive know-how, Ben's jealousy has him convinced that he has to out-do Kevin before the older boy influences Vin to embrace his bad-guy side at a charity race.

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Party Animal
description: Green Arrow, who is determined to finally throw a successful holiday party for the Justice League, finds his plans thwarted when Plastic Man brings a tranquilized super villain to the gathering.

title: A Sticky Situation
description: All Ben wants to do is stop Queen Bee from robbing a bank, but when Kevin shows up to try and be the hero and take all the glory himself, Ben will need to save the day twice or end up in hot honey.

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: Thunderhowl Part 2
description: Released after eons of imprisonment, Thunderhowl helps Bee and Chromia navigate the dangerous Crystal City.

title: Wiped Out Part 1
description: Out in space to catch some solar waves, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor discover the asteroid remains of a mysterious planet.

title: Brain Freeze
description: When a mysterious new ice cream flavor takes Townsville by storm, the girls suspect there might be foul play.

title: El Candidato
description: Un grupo de niños quedan encerrados en la escuela luego de la gala de caridad de sus padres. Designan a Gumball como líder encargado de sacarlos de ahí, pero la situación se convierte en un caos.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Bad Heir Day
description: Princess Zange's Autostyle Magisword is stolen and it's up to the Warriors to retrieve it so their royal leader can face her subjects without bad hair.

title: Panda 2
description: Baby Panda happily lives in a closed off environment for study. But when he's given a new friend, Panda 2, his worldview is shaken, which sets him off on a great adventure.

title: One Space Day at a Time
description: The guys are now in space.

title: Papel de Bano Bebecin
description: Manzana necesita conseguir la provisión del papel higiénico que usaría en toda su vida para terminar su escultura de arte moderno.

title: Wicked Shades
description: When Pizza Steve borrows Uncle Grandpa's sunglasses, he sees things in a whole new light.

title: Old School
description: Mega Man must stop Chaotique from making Silicon Central disappear, as in literally erasing the school at a subatomic level, while learning life lessons from a rambling old-bot named Hal.

title: Magnus P.I.
description: There's a been a string of thefts and each one has involved a Bakugan. The AAAnimus security force have decided the only brawler who could be responsible is: Magnus. The shock of this accusation sets Magnus off to takes justice in his own hands and go after the thief himself./Magnus foils the latest burglary attempt by the phantom thief, and in doing so, discovers the brawler partners with a golden Bakugan.  Magnus is now more interested in a brawl, than stopping any crime.

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: Hat Trick
description: When Felix Faust steals Zatanna's magical top hat, the Justice League must help retrieve it before the evil wizard can use it to create a magic portal, releasing the demon Ghast.
